            <thetext>The generator only evaluates asset hints once in a run. This includes expansion 
of asset-let macros. If a subsequent job uses the same classes, but with 
different asset-let bindings, they are not honored. This shows e.g. in the 
Widgetbrowser, where the first job, source-script-classic, uses Oxygen icons, 
but source-script-modern and -simple use Tango icons. These are not honored in 
the script&#39;s resource info.</thetext>
